WEBVTT

00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:32.280
I spent a whole night
on the floor of our basement bathroom.

00:06:33.240 --> 00:06:36.616
I alternated between cooling
my feverish head

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:38.320
against the ceramic tiles

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:43.200
and trying violently to throw up
despite not having eaten anything in days.

00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:47.056
When Sadiye found me
at the end of the night

00:06:47.080 --> 00:06:48.376
she was horrified,

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:49.800
and we got back on the phone.

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:51.536
We called everyone.

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:55.376
We called surgeons and pain docs
and general practitioners --

00:06:55.400 --> 00:06:57.936
anyone we could find on the internet,

00:06:57.960 --> 00:07:00.000
and not a single one of them
would help me.